Author: David S Fischer [aut, cre], Fabian J Theis [ctb], Nir Yosef [ctb]
Maintainer: David S Fischer <david.fischer@helmholtz-muenchen.de>
Description: LineagePulse can perform longitudinal differential expression analysis based on pseudotime as a continuous covariate. Moreover, LineagePulse can perform differential expression analysis between discrete groups of cells and based on a mixture model (including responsive subset analysis, RSA).
